sectionText: Enrollment restricted to current actuarial science majors until approximately 4:00pm on November 17th . Prospective transfers should review http://www.math.illinois.edu/ActuarialScience/transfer-to-actsci-ui-only.pdf Prospective transfers who are not able to register on or after November 17th should fill out the form here to be added to the request list: http://go.illinois.edu/SP17Math210  .
